h="170" style="display:block;border:0;max-width:170px;width:100%;height:auto;" alt="Oyabun Tattoo" src="https://jviaxe.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_6a3bfa96617ed85bcc5a755c7e8d8864/images/logo_trans.png"><p style="margin:12px 0 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#111111;">8199 Clairemont Mesa Blvd., Suite L<br>San Diego, CA 92111<br>(858) 384-6099<br>contact@oyabuntattoo.com</p><p style="margin:12px 0 0;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/yushitattoo/"><img height="32" style="display:inline-block;border:0;" alt="Instagram" src="https://jviaxe.stripocdn.email/content/assets/img/social-icons/circle-black/instagram-circle-black.png"></a></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:10px 20px 18px;" align="center"><p style="margin:0;font-size:10px;line-height:1.4;color:#333333;"><a style="color:#333333;" href="https://www.oyabuntattoo.com">WWW.OYABUNTATTOO.COM</a> @ OYABUN TATTOO</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>$$,
